<!-- Solutions -->
<section class="section bg-cream">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header centered">
            <span class="section-eyebrow">Solutions</span>
            <h2>Irrigation Solutions for the Recycling Industry</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="three-col-grid">
            <div class="info-card">
                <div class="info-card-icon">♻️</div>
                <h3>Leachate Land Application</h3>
                <p>Sub-surface drip application of landfill or compost leachate on buffer land eliminates discharge to storm sewers and surface water — turning a liability into a resource.</p>
                <ul class="check-list">
                    <li>NSF 245 certified driplines</li>
                    <li>High-nitrogen leachate compatible</li>
                    <li>Automated loading rate controls</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="info-card">
                <div class="info-card-icon">🌡️</div>
                <h3>Compost Windrow Moisture Control</h3>
                <p>Maintain optimal moisture (50–60% by weight) in compost windrows using overhead sprinklers or dripline tubes placed between rows — accelerating decomposition and quality.</p>
                <ul class="check-list">
                    <li>Overhead and inline moisture delivery</li>
                    <li>Moisture sensor integration</li>
                    <li>Automated based on turning schedules</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="info-card">
                <div class="info-card-icon">💨</div>
                <h3>Facility Dust Suppression</h3>
                <p>Tipping floor, sorting lines, and conveyor transfer points generate particulate dust. Our misting systems suppress dust at the source with minimal water.</p>
                <ul class="check-list">
                    <li>Fog nozzle misting bars</li>
                    <li>Recirculating water option</li>
                    <li>Belt-triggered automatic operation</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="info-card">
                <div class="info-card-icon">🌿</div>
                <h3>Buffer Zone Revegetation</h3>
                <p>Establish and maintain vegetative buffers and screen plantings around facilities using drip irrigation systems — improving community relations and permit compliance.</p>
                <ul class="check-list">
                    <li>Dripline and drip tape options</li>
                    <li>Leachate reuse compatible</li>
                    <li>Low-maintenance automated systems</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="info-card">
                <div class="info-card-icon">🏗️</div>
                <h3>Landfill Cap Vegetation</h3>
                <p>Maintain vegetation on closed landfill caps to control erosion, manage cap moisture, and satisfy post-closure care requirements.</p>
                <ul class="check-list">
                    <li>Lightweight installation over cap liner</li>
                    <li>Shallow-depth installation options</li>
                    <li>Freeze-resistant components available</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="highlight-card">
                <div class="info-card-icon">📋</div>
                <h3>Regulatory Compliance Package</h3>
                <p>We provide complete documentation for 40 CFR 503, state solid waste permits, and air quality compliance — including engineering calculations and monitoring reports.</p>
                <a href="/contact" class="btn-outline-dark mt-md">Request Compliance Consultation</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

